{"type": "article", "id": 11405, "title": "Recto-Verso 灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-30T12:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000134qwn570xviAMtadEK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t自从 OLED 技术慢慢发展成熟后，灯饰设计有了更多可能性，设计师也有了更多奇思妙想。比如 Bina Baitel 设计工作室在今年米兰设计周上带来的这一系列 Recto-Verso 灯饰。它最具趣味的部分是，用户可以像拉窗帘一般将它慢慢掀起来，控制照明的亮度以及适合空间氛围的光线，创建了用户与产品之间越来越强的互动性。Recto-Verso 是用可折叠的 OLED 灯管组成的，外层包覆着一层皮革，皮革的恶颜色有粉色、芬兰、红色、土耳其蓝等多种选择，细节纹路清晰，挂置在空间中也给人温暖的感觉。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000132BmrS7su8d6ZjPv0V.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.84285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000133NOEH5miZ8Jzb1dkc.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.94857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000133GDaCFuA0LeWrBYZm.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000134nXZ8TJEt3F1hNgxr.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.70714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}